title: Add AAVE and aAAVE on Avalanche voting power on Snapshot
body:
The Aave protocol embrace the EVM multiverse strategy to make DeFi accessible on multiple chains for a diverse audience.

Currently only AAVE on the polygon network can vote on snapshot creating a discrimination towards Avalanche community members

This vote intends to fix this and give Avalanche users a voice.
choices: Yes add AVAX AAVE and aAAVE vote
author: 0x329c54289Ff5D6B7b7daE13592C6B1EDA1543eD4
